The '''First Administrator''' was the head of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[New Republic General Ministry|General Ministry]]. The First Administrator was charged with setting down the protocol of the Ministry, and funneled information from the General Ministry to the [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of Sate]] or [[Minister of State]], as well as the [[Ruling Council]] and the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]].

[[Nanaod Engh]] served as First Administrator during the [[Black Fleet Crisis]].

